**验收条件缺失**:

| 验收条件 | 状态 |
|----------|------|
| GenerateRoomPassword 使用 crypto/rand 生成安全随机数 | ❌ 未实现 |
| Hash 计算为 SHA256(ip + port + randomNumber) | ❌ 未实现 |
| 返回 32 字符的十六进制字符串（前 16 字节） | ❌ 未实现 |
| 单元测试验证输出格式和随机性 | ❌ 未实现 |
| 两次调用产生不同密码（随机性测试） | ❌ 未实现 |

**建议实现**:
```go
import (
    "crypto/rand"
    "crypto/sha256"
    "encoding/hex"
    "fmt"
)

// GenerateRoomPassword generates a cryptographically secure room password.
// It concatenates ip, port, and a random 16-byte number, then hashes with SHA256.
func GenerateRoomPassword(ip, port string) (string, error) {
    randomBytes := make([]byte, 16)
    if _, err := rand.Read(randomBytes); err != nil {
        return "", fmt.Errorf("failed to generate random bytes: %w", err)
    }
    
    data := []byte(ip + port)
    data = append(data, randomBytes...)
    
    hash := sha256.Sum256(data)
    // Return first 16 bytes (16 bytes = 32 hex chars)
    return hex.EncodeToString(hash[:16]), nil
}
```

**需要的测试**:
```go
func TestGenerateRoomPassword_Format(t *testing.T) {
    pwd, err := GenerateRoomPassword("192.168.1.1", "8080")
    if err != nil {
        t.Fatalf("unexpected error: %v", err)
    }
    if len(pwd) != 32 {
        t.Fatalf("expected 32 hex chars, got %d", len(pwd))
    }
    if !regexp.MustCompile(`^[0-9a-f]{32}$`).MatchString(pwd) {
        t.Fatalf("invalid hex format: %s", pwd)
    }
}

func TestGenerateRoomPassword_Randomness(t *testing.T) {
    pwd1, _ := GenerateRoomPassword("192.168.1.1", "8080")
    pwd2, _ := GenerateRoomPassword("192.168.1.1", "8080")
    if pwd1 == pwd2 {
        t.Fatal("two calls produced same password")
    }
}

